Body: Description: After we run the Group Probable Owners job and the report gets emailed. We only get 5000 rows. There are many more rows that we can not see. And the app only shows 1000.  Is there a way to get the entire report results?
@Frantz Baptiste​ There is a limit set in the Report config by default that can be removed/increased:
What We've Learned Updated: The customer noticed a limitation in the number of rows in the report.
